## CATEGORY 4: RIDE-HAILING & MAPS

### üöó UBER (Best map-based interface)

**Why study Uber**: Shows how to layer UI elements OVER a map without
creating chaos. The interface is minimal because the map provides context.

#### Visual Hierarchy Strategy:
```
Home (requesting a ride):
LAYER 1: Map ‚Äî FULL SCREEN, IS the background
LAYER 2: Search bar ‚Äî "Where to?" at the top, floating on the map
LAYER 3: Quick action pills ‚Äî Home, Work, recent places
LAYER 4: Bottom sheet ‚Äî ride options, price, ETA

